Done. One breaking issue found and fixed:

**Dockerfile.media** тАФ `npm ci --omit=dev` excluded `typescript` from install, so `npx tsc` would crash at Docker image build time. Fixed with a proper multi-stage build: `build` stage installs all deps and compiles, `runtime` stage copies the compiled `dist/` and installs only prod deps.

All else was clean:
- `tsc --noEmit` passes with zero errors
- No pre-commit hooks (only `.sample` hooks in `.git/hooks/`)
- No test scripts in `media-engine/package.json`
- All imports resolve correctly across all 7 source files
- `audio-safety.ts` and `combinator.ts` are standalone utility modules (not wired into the queue by design тАФ used at the agent/orchestration layer)
